Dialogs.Dialog: When did you grow up so much！？ And that apron is...
Rinko
Because... I'm your wife. I have grown up and that's why I'm wearing an apron.
My wife！？ You mean we are married！？
You're such a weird guy... Hey, are you still half asleep？ If you don't hurry up, you'll be late for work.
Oh no！ I'm late！ Then I'm leaving！
Dear！！
W-What？
What do you want to eat for your dinner？
I'm in a hurry！ We don't have to talk about that now.
No！ It's the duty of a wife to cook delicious food for her husband.
What do you want for dinner tonight？ Japanese food？ Western？ Or Chinese？ Or...
Whatever is fine！ Just decide by your own！
R-Right. I'm such a useless woman who can't even think of dinner by herself. I'm not qualified to be your wife！
Don't exaggerate！
Then do you hate me？ Do you still love me like this？
I don't hate you and I still love you！
Rinko is happy！
You're okay now, right？ I'll get going.
Geez！ You forget to wear your wedding ring！ You're so careless...
Ring！？ Oh, but I'm in such a hurry today！
You must have other women, right！？ Now, I am like a piece of garbage waiting to be dumped！
I'm not going to dump you！ I am not！ Okay, I'll wear the ring！
Really？ Rinko is happy！
I'm already late, so I have to leave now.
Dear！！
What is it this time！？
Did you forget a goodbye kiss？
Kiss！？
You do it every morning. Come on, chu~
W-Wait a sec！ Hey, it's time I have to be at work...！
As I thought...！ You don't love me anymore...
I love you！ I love you, so please let me go to work！！
Really！？ Then can you say "Ai-shi-te-ru" (I love you) to me a million times？
(If I don't say "Ai-shi-te- ru" million times, she won't let me go to work...)
I love you... (Still 999,999 times left.)
I love you... (Still 999,998 times left.)
I love you... (Still 999,997 times left.)
I love you... (Still 999,996 times left.)
I love you... (Still 999,995 times left.)
Argh, cut it out！！
Ta-da♪
I love you... I love you... I love you...
Phew... This is already the 965,730th time...
Huh...？ It was a dream？ Getting married isn't too bad... Maybe？
(“I love you！” 1,000,000th time...)
ＨＩＮＴ
Say to the microphone “Ai-shi-te-ru！”
Hmm...？ ▲小早川＊▲！？
Rinko
Ah, you finally came to.
Hmm... Huh？ By the way, where are we！？
Where？ We're on a deserted island.
D-Deserted island！？ How did we end up here？
In the end, the only people who washed ashore on this island are you and Rinko...
Just the two of us on this deserted island！？
There was that weird light and then there were some sort of germs leaked from a research lab. Something like what we usually see in cheesy movies...
So you mean to say there are unusual phenomena all around the world？
Right... And in the end, you and I are the only human beings left in this world...
Just the two of us！？ What do we do from now on...？
Sorry... It's Rinko's fault...
Your fault...？ What do you mean by that, ▲小早川＊▲！？
This is the world that Rinko wished for...
Why did you wish for this kind of world...？
For me, no one wants me... No one can understand me... So I just want to be alone by myself.
I prayed to God for solitude. I wanted to be isolated from others.
And it ended up like this. Now that everyone else has vanished, I can have the solitude I've wished for...
God must have punished me for making that kind of wish.
You've just become my boyfriend and I dragged you into this mess. I'm sorry...
God didn't punish you. At least, you are not alone in this world, ▲小早川＊▲.
We are entrusted to create a new world...
From now on, we both must do our best to live on in this world！
I see... Now I'm not lonely anymore, because I have you...
Let's do our best to live on. We are in charge of making a new world！
A dream？ The world with just the two of us, huh, ▲小早川＊▲...？
Rinko
Nya... nya...
An abandoned cat？ ...No, it's, ▲小早川＊▲！？
Nya, nya！
What happened！？ Why are you...
Nya~...
Sorry, I don't understand what you're saying...
Nya, nya, nya！
You want me to play with you？
Nya~♪
Then I'll try patting you, okay？
Kyaaa！
Oh... She seems to hate this...
Grrrrrrr！
Not the tail, huh...？
Nya...！
I think that's her weak spot...
Meo~~w....
Hahaha, in a good mood, huh？
Are these whiskers real？
Nya~！
Oh, cool！
They can be stretched...
Kyaaa~！
Sorry！ Did it hurt...？
That's enough！
You can talk！！
Rinko the kitten was so cute...
(That ball... Shall I touch it？)
(Are the ears real？ I'm curious...)
(Since she is a cat, will she be wary if I touch her tail？)
(Speaking of cats, the chin causes... rumbling.)
(Will touching her beard make her angry？)
ＨＩＮＴ
Touch the paws
Touch ears
Touch the tail
Touch the chin
Pull the beard
Rinko
Lucky Magical~♪ Lucky Magical Girl Rinko is here to make your life better！
▲小早川＊▲！？ What's wrong？ Why are you dressed like that！？
Don't you know？ This "Lucky Magical Girl Rinko" is a very popular show on TV！
Lucky Magical Girl Rinko？ It's some sort of a magical girl show？
Yeah, that's right.
I see... And that must be the magical wand！
Huh？ Ah, this one is a stick.
I use this to strike the bad guys.
A stick... Ouch！ Ouch...
Bang！ Bang！ Boom！ Boom！ Just like that！
I-It hurts！ Stop it！
Well, it's something like that.
...And what's with this look？ Did you do the transformation, like the ones with the hearts or star beams and stuff...？
Transformation？ How could I possibly do that？ I just simply changed my clothes.
Changed your clothes？ So this is just a cosplay？
Cosplay？ Do I look like someone who would do that kind of thing？
Well, you don't.
What's that heart-shaped thing？
Cutie box.
Hmm？ What do you use it for？
Well... I don't really know much. Someone named "S-pon-sor" told me to carry it.
(So it's a toy for grade school girls, huh？)
What's that necklace with a bell on it？
When this thing shines, I'll know that someone is calling for me.
But it's shining now. Don't you have to go？
I'll just skip it... I feel kind of sluggish today.
Is it okay like that！？
Ah... Don't you touch my costume. It's a rental item.
You don't even have one for your own, huh...？
By the way, since you're a magical girl, don't you have that thing... I mean, that tiny animal as your sidekick？
I don't. We had a budget cut, so we have to be stingy.
Really？ Then what is that thing on the left screen？
Huh...？
What？ You got it！ Hmm...？ A Daruma doll？ This is so original.
That's my dad.
Y-Your dad！？
Daruma
I'm Magical Girl Rinko's dad.
I'm sorry, Dad！ Rinko-san has always been taking good care of me.
Hmm！ Hmmmmmmmmmm！！ So, it's you！ You are the one who hangs out with Rinko until late every night, huh！？
Yes, this guy is Rinko's boyfriend.
I never intended to hang out with her that late...
No excuse！ I just can't forgive a guy who confuses my daughter！
Rinko！ Punish him with that thing！
Okay~！
My dad is angry now, so just bear with this beam for a bit, okay？
W-What！？ What beam？
Lucky Magical~♪
Nooooooooooooo！ P-Please forgive me！！
Urgh... Well, of course, it was just a dream...
But a show like that would definitely be cancelled in no time.
(A Magical Girl！ That's the costume she's wearing.)
(The bell on the neck is shining...)
ＨＩＮＴ
Touch the costume
Touch the bell
Touch the cutie oval
Why did you become this small ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Well... You are so cute with that outfit...
(Urgh... She doesn't talk to me.)
Did your Mama tie the ribbons for you？
(This is no good... I should find a topic to talk with her about...)
(Not this one...)
That doll is cute.
...Yeah.
(Oh！ She's speaking to me now！)
What is her name？
...Emily-chan.
Let's be friends, Emily-chan！
Fine... I guess.
Then we are friends！ Will Rinko-chan be my friend, too？
(Oh no！ I probably said something bad.)
Emily-chan asked if you wanted to play house...
Ah, okay. I wanna play！
Then Rinko will be Mama.
I will be Papa then.
Okay, fine...
Then let's start from when Papa comes home from work, okay？
No. Papa's always busy with work. Papa doesn't come home.
I see. But today Papa finished work early, so Papa is coming home.
...Then that's fine.
Then let's start... I'm home~.
Oh！ You came home early today. It will surely rain tomorrow then.
Hahaha...
Um, let's do it again from the beginning... I'm home~.
Welcome home, my dear. Do you want ninder first or take a wowsher first？
("Ninder"？ "Wowsher"？)
What is ninder？ Papa doesn't quite understand...
Don't know. Rinko's Papa always says "Is ninder ready？" when he arrives home.
I see... I still don't get it but I think I'll have ninder first.
Sorry. I didn't know that you would be home early. I didn't prepare it for you.
Ahaha... So there's no ninder for Papa, huh？
Ah, please don't forget to make a maypent.
("Maypent"？)
Last time, you said you had to go on a nusibess trip with your pomcany, didn't you？
？？ Rinko-chan's family sure talks in a very mysterious way, huh？
No, only Papa does. He definitely isn't Japanese.
Really？
...Rinko hates Papa！
Saying that makes Papa seem very pitiful.
It's fine！ Papa treats Mama badly！ That's why Rinko hates him！
But Rinko loves Mama！
And this outfit. Mama made it, you know？ It looks the same as Emily-chan's. Hehe...
Yeah, it looks exactly the same. Your Mama is very kind, right？
Yes！ Mama is very good at making clothes！
When Rinko gets married, Mama will make a wedding dress for Rinko too！
I see... I can't wait to see Rinko-chan as a bride.
Yeah！
That was... ▲小早川＊▲...？
I wonder if she had grown up with such lonely memories...
(That doll looks very important...)
ＨＩＮＴ
Touch the doll
？ Where is this...？
That girl with the white hat... Somehow, she looks transparent...
Girl
I've been looking for you.
You've finally come here.
This is the first time we have met, isn't it？
No, your memory hasn't gotten in order yet. Come on. Take a deep breath...
This smells like... Lavender？
Yes... You remember...
But I don't even know where this place is...
This is a place in your memories where time moves backward... It's a special place...
Wait a minute...
Hehe... Ah... Hey！ Can you see it？
Summer, under the blue sky, we played by the river. We walked in the sunflower fields. We listened to cicadas cry.
I feel like I've forgotten something...
Well, that's okay. I have to go now.
I see... I will remember you forever.
You don't have to remember me. Just put me somewhere in your memories...
Rinko
Then... Whenever you can't remember me, just ask these lavenders.
Eh？
There's a flower language for lavender！ Hmph！
Lavender's flower language is, "I am waiting for you."
"I am waiting for you"？ Eh？
I think it'll be fine, but I should not make her feel lonely in the future. I promise you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Gaaah！ Death Genome！ They have planned to invade the Earth... Argh... They've come this far...！
Arggggggghhhhh！
W-What is that robot！？
Rinko
Everyone in the Earth Defense Force, from here on, just leave it to me！
Y-You are Rintaro！ Hah！ ...Could that be...
Volvavin...！？ No way！ The prototype production is complete！？
Stand up, Volvavin！
Grrrrrrr！
All right！ Let's go！
Take this！ Volve Kick~！！
Yes！！ The Volve Kick！ How's that, Death Genome！？
Whooooosh...
Ahhhhhhhhh！！
What was that...！？ The Volve Kick couldn't do anything to him！
Whooooosssshhhh！
Waaaaaah！
Ah！ Volvavin！！
Urgh...
Volvavi~~nnn！！
What's wrong！？ Move！ Move now！
What is that！？ Now, Volvavin can't move！
Of course, the real battle has just started...
Waaaaaaaaah！！
Rintaro-kun！ It's too dangerous. You must leave Volvavin now！！
Do I have to leave...？ Do I have to leave...？ Do I have to leave~~~~！？
Mom
(Rintaro...)
(Rintaro... Please, open your eyes.)
Mom...！
(Now... We shall join forces to bring down Death Genome！)
Yes！
(Now is the time I shall grant you my power... Now, shout "Volve Fusion"！)
Volve Fusion~~~！！
Grrrrrrrrrr！
I can feel it...！ Rintaro-kun and Volvavin are now synchronized！
Right！ The Super Robot Warrior Volvavin was built using a mix of the DNA of Rintaro-kun's mother.
Now, it's using the spirit of a mother who wants to protect her daughter！
Now！ Volvavin！
Volve Missiles！！
You did it！ Volvavin！ Rintaro-kun！
We did it... Mom！
...Thanks, Volvavin！
Volve Fusion~~~~！！ Yes！ Volvavin is the best...
Rinko
...Hey, are you listening？
Eh？
...Did you fall asleep？
Sorry.
Hah... Are you fully awake now？
Yup, perfectly.
Then let's continue... The world we are in now, the feelings we feel, could they possibly be just a dream...？
...But now I can really see you, and feel you, ▲小早川＊▲.
If I reach out my hand, I can touch you. This feeling tells me that it's real.
The feeling you mentioned is just a perception of your brain. What if your brain is also dreaming...？
That's...
There's no proof at all. Who knows if you are now awake or you are still dreaming... No one knows...
A dream is what your subconsciousness creates. It shows you what you want to see...
What do you mean？
In other words...
For Rinko to be with you like this, it's probably Rinko's subconsciousness that created this world.
It can't be...
In this ideal world where you are this close to Rinko, Rinko would be overly happy.
Since it's a dream, you are allowed to do anything you want.
Rinko could be very selfish and you would just laugh it off... It's this wonderful world that Rinko wishes for...
I also wish for such a wonderful world.
Is it your wish？
Yeah, seeing you being able to do what you want is also my happiness, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hehe.
Eh？
If that's what makes you happy, then your subconsciousness can create such a dream for you...
Ah...
(No good... I don't know why I'm getting so sleepy.)
What？ Are you going to sleep again？
Yeah, sorry... I can't...
It would be nice if you saw a nice dream...
Rinko also had a dream today... A dream where Rinko was with you...
The sun behind you was shining so brightly...
There was a long tunnel coming from the sun...
And then there was a strong wind gushing out...
Rinko couldn't stand firmly...
...I fell asleep while talking with you again, eh, ▲小早川＊▲？
And is this still a dream？ So it's a dream within a dream...？
But the feel of my pillow in my room here... It must be real...
Oh no！ The one before was a dream！ This is reality then... I think...
Finally, that's the last leaf left on the tree.
Rinko
Eh！？
That withering tree... Its leaves are rapidly disappearing... Just like my life.
If you say something like that, you won't be able to recover.
I'm just saying the truth. I can feel myself getting weaker day-by-day, ▲小早川＊▲...
Liar, I won't listen to you. I won't believe in such nonsense.
Like myself, the tree was full of green leaves when I entered this hospital. Now, we are only waiting for our end...
We'll get you healed. We'll buy some new medicine, okay？
Even if we change the medicine, it will only stop the pain. It won't cure my illness.
You will get better, I said！You'll only be defeated by your illness with such a weak heart.
You are so kind. But, I already understand. I won't last any longer, ▲小早川＊▲.
Now... I wonder who will shed a tear for me when I leave.
Rinko will cry. Because Rinko... Rinko will always love you forever.
You must be saying that for me because my life is ending soon.
Of course not！ You are the most precious person for me in this whole world...
That's why... Don't leave Rinko alone！
I'm so happy. But I don't have much time left.
I beg you. Don't say such things！ I will do anything for you！ I will ask any doctor to come and cure you！ So...
You are still young. You will be loved, and you should live your life happily forever, ▲小早川＊▲.
I don't want to... Rinko can never love anyone else but you...！
I am so glad that I have here by my side in my final moment. I can go peacefully while holding your warm hands, ▲小早川＊▲...
I will never forgive you if you die. That's why... Stop saying such cruel things.
Haha... As usual, you're such a selfish girl, ▲小早川＊▲.
Yes. I'm selfish... Just believe in me. I'll surely find a way to cure you. I won't give up...
Come here... ▲小早川＊▲.
Don't cry, okay？
If you are not with me...
...Please. Stop crying, okay？
...Okay.
I'm so glad that I met you. It's due to my beautiful memories with you that I don't fear anything anymore ▲小早川＊▲.
You should carry on even when I'm gone, okay？ Please promise me, ▲小早川＊▲....
Promise me, okay？ You should always be the one I admire, always cheerful, and always honest ▲小早川＊▲.
...I'm so glad. ...This way... I can leave peacefully...
Ah, the last leaf has finally been blown away by the wind... Goodbye, ▲小早川＊▲...
▲小早川＊▲... Thank you.
No~~！
*sniff* *sniff* ▲小早川＊▲... Goodbye...
*sniff* ...Eh？ What's with these tears！？
Lately, I've felt so weak...
(Crying... I have to wipe tears)
ＨＩＮＴ
Wipe the tears
(Today is the first live show presented by ▲小早川＊▲...)
(Finally, your dreams came true after all these years, ▲小早川＊▲...)
(You are an official member of the Killer Bambies ▲小早川＊▲...)
Rinko
Make some noise！
More！
More！！
Yay！
Phew...
Good evening, we are the Killer Bambies.
(Great！ It's so great... ▲小早川＊▲！)
Um... What to say...
Ah, yeah...
First of all, we'd like to thank you all for gathering here tonight.
And then... to the God of the Deth Jabbi...
For giving me meaning for my once good-for-nothing life, my lowest gratitude...
Tonight, we will go all out until you collapse...
And then... Hmm, I don't know anymore...
All of you aren't here to hear my preaching, right？
Okay.
My name is Rinko.
The Killer Bambies' Rinko.
I'll expect you to come with me, to the deepest pits of hell.
(Even though I'm watching her from the front row...)
(I don't know why the stage seems to be so far away...)
(▲小早川＊▲... She just seems to be far away...)
(Did she just look this way？)
(It's all right...)
(We are always connected to each other...)
(However different the position is, however far the distance is, they all don't matter...)
(It's because we are one, isn't it？)
I love you！
...Eh？ A dream？
Even in my dreams, you surely shine brightly ▲小早川＊▲...
(It's getting really exciting！ “Yes”)

Shout “iee！！” to the microphone
